ss how to efficiently pick the\nreference temperatures. For uniformly sampled temperatures (between a minimum\nand maximum temperature), we conduct a sensitivity study which led us to use\nsix temperatures. We ran both local (Pattern Search, PS) and global (Particle\nSwarm Optimization, PSO) gradient-free optimization methods.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Aug 2020 14:50:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 24 Sep 2020 18:53:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-06"}
